I"p<p>Stranded is a <strong>2D platformer</strong> where the player slings themselves around planets to get to their spaceship. It was developed for <a href="https://itch.io/jam/blackthornprodgamejam2">Blackthornprod Game Jam #2</a>. The game contains 3 levels, each on a different planet with varying level of difficulty, with the first planet acting as a tutorial level.
<!--more--></p>

<p>The game was built using the <strong>Unity3D</strong> engine and written in <strong>C#</strong>. I worked in a <strong>team of five</strong> on this, as a <strong>gameplay programmer</strong>, including the <strong>slinging functionality</strong> which was inspired by the bash functionality in Ori and the Blind Forest.</p>

